{"tid":1275041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組行動原則: 正面宣傳 鞏固成果 堅定信念 同時請登報組準備宣言","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:47:26.000Z","uid":35776,"like":155,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"402f2c34f813f7b018142ab90805346e79bcc629","tid":1275041,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣組</span><br />\n<br />\n一 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>正面宣傳</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本日行動過程整體和平，秩序良好，且成果豐厚，成功於立法會內朗讀宣言，正式向世界宣讀香港人共有心聲，為香港史上民主運動未有之功，乃香港人同心協力之果，需大力正面宣傳，揚我義士英勇不懈。<br />\n<br />\n二 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>鞏固成果</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n本日行為本港史上未見，立下香港民主運動之新章，重新定義民主運動，我輩必須再三鞏固成果，包括並不限於: <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>在世上廣泛傳播香港宣言及其精神，並使之成為世人之共有認知</strong></span>，並須<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>重定和平民主運動之基調</strong></span>，主動掌握輿論，莫使我輩重墮由過去運動所建立，由本次運動<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>打破的精神枷鎖，避免再次自我設限</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n三 <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>堅定信念</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n鞏固成果同時，莫忘<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>堅定我輩信念</strong></span>，莫使一人忘形，莫使一人喪志，為未來所有行動作心理準備，乃是<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>修心壯志</strong></span>之心靈武裝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">登報組</span><br />\n<br />\n登報組請早作準備製圖登報，將宣言公告天下，以防國際傳媒有所遺漏或不及報導，可將宣言中英文版本交預外國傳媒，並以頭版登報以補缺漏。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹在此拜首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />向三位烈士，一眾前線，後援，協作義士及全體香港人致意！！！！！！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f3f2e78cba0f52a935a7eef55851958f4cbf441","tid":1275041,"uid":61281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:58:35.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"9cfbd1256c487b1542de4dd5b7e80bda859d97c2","tid":1275041,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"義士做嘅嘢有冇用就係睇文宣出幾多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdfa47999f53355389bfe02c683301e0754a682","tid":1275041,"uid":66325,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"【有圖可airdrop】請廣傳！2019年7月1日 屬於香港人嘅《香港人宣言》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望大家有用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzjcn3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpzjcn3b.png&h=03e80e63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7hA5gw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7hA5gw.png&h=43a4df2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xi40wWx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxi40wWx.png&h=3a25bf1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9oP9Jc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9oP9Jc.png&h=f84ace31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4rVkPT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4rVkPT.png&h=9d7743e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpfOFPT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpfOFPT.png&h=7e787a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nP1uqgy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt